OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,FBen Bason reports on the ongoing
OL,7,Fimpact of Covid-19, five years after
OL,8,Fthe first UK case was recorded in York
OL,10,FA former vet says she has left her
OL,11,Fhouse just once in two years after
OL,12,Fdeveloping "life-decimating" long
OL,13,FCovid.
OL,15,FFran Haddock, 34, from Sheffield, was
OL,16,Fan amateur triathlete and was training
OL,17,Ffor a marathon before she developed
OL,18,Fchronic fatigue syndrome after
OL,19,Fcatching coronavirus in November 2022.
