OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,FSince then she has been left unable to
OL,7,Fwork and almost completely bedbound,
OL,8,Fwith debilitating weakness and chronic
OL,9,Fvertigo as well as fatigue.
OL,11,F"I can't walk or stand I can only
OL,12,Fleave my room once a day for the
OL,13,Ftoilet," she said.
OL,15,F"I have to use a commode next to my
OL,16,Fbed and I'm fully reliant on care from
OL,17,Fmy family. It's unimaginable unless
OL,18,Fyou've been through it. It's life-
OL,19,Fdecimating basically."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
