OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,FFellow long Covid sufferer Paula Dean,
OL,7,Fan army veteran, considered taking her
OL,8,Fown life after she was left bedridden
OL,9,Ffor six weeks and forced off work for
OL,10,Feight months after she caught Covid
OL,11,Ffor the third time.
OL,13,F"I became incredibly depressed," she
OL,14,Fsaid. "To the point where I just
OL,15,Fdidn't want to be here any more. I
OL,16,Fcouldn't live. If this was my life
OL,17,Fthen I didn't want that life."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
