OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,FAn estimated two million people in the
OL,7,FUK suffer from long Covid, a term used
OL,8,Fto describe ongoing symptoms of Covid-
OL,9,F19, or new symptoms that develop after
OL,10,Fa Covid-19 infection.
OL,12,FSufferers can experience a wide range
OL,13,Fof symptoms, including fatigue,
OL,14,Fdifficulty concentrating, muscle ache
OL,15,Fand shortness of breath.
OL,17,FResearch remains ongoing and the NHS
OL,18,Fhas specialist clinics to investigate
OL,19,Fthe condition and help sufferers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
