OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,FTracy Evans-Phillips attends a clinic
OL,7,Fin Doncaster, using playing cards to
OL,8,Fhelp with memory problems she
OL,9,Fdeveloped after contracting the virus.
OL,11,FShe said: "I've been having lots of
OL,12,Fdifficulty in conversations, where I'm
OL,13,Fmeant to be remember somebody's name
OL,14,For to remember do something. So I've
OL,15,Fhad to now rely on writing lots of
OL,16,Fthings down using my calendar so I
OL,17,Fdon't forget things in the future."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
