OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,FKaren South, clinical lead at the
OL,7,FDoncaster Long Covid Team, said: "I
OL,8,Fthink I probably speak on behalf of
OL,9,Fall long Covid clinicians - it's been
OL,10,Ftrial and error.
OL,12,F"So at the beginning, it was just
OL,13,Fputting in the treatment pathways and
OL,14,Fassessment approaches that we thought
OL,15,Fwe would need to by using the therapy
OL,16,Fskills we've already got as therapists
OL,17,Fand clinicians and then listening to
OL,18,Fpatients and learning from patients."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
