OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,FDr Heidi Baseler, of Hull York Medical
OL,7,FSchool, has studied the effects of
OL,8,FCovid on brain function. She said:
OL,9,F"There's a lack of interest, or a loss
OL,10,Fof interest, in Covid and long Covid
OL,11,Fbecause we have sort of moved on as a
OL,12,Fsociety and decided we're not
OL,13,Finterested in it any more... Funding
OL,14,Fhas dried up."
OL,16,FMs Haddock is among those calling on
OL,17,Fthe government to invest more in
OL,18,Fresearch.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
