OL,3,C'I've left the house once in two years
OL,4,Cdue to long Covid'
OL,6,F"We need the government not just to be
OL,7,Ftalking the talk but walking the walk
OL,8,Fwhen it comes to research and
OL,9,Ffunding," she said.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,12,FHealth said: "No single treatment
OL,13,Fcurrently exists for long Covid, which
OL,14,Fis why we provide funding for more
OL,15,Fresearch into the condition including
OL,16,Fclinical trials to test and compare
OL,17,Fdifferent treatments."
